to \fBCtrl+C\fP\&. It will copy only if there is a selection and send an
interrupt otherwise. Similarly, \X'tty: link #action-copy_and_clear_or_interrupt'\fI\%copy_and_clear_or_interrupt\fP\X'tty: link' will copy
