.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
To get the command output that was last accessed by a keyboard action or mouse
action:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
map f1 show_last_visited_command_output
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
