.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B New window
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
map ctrl+shift+enter new_window
map cmd+enter new_window üçé
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
You can open a new \X'tty: link #term-window'\fI\%kitty window\fP\X'tty: link' running an arbitrary program,
